http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7439563/how-to-ssh-to-localhost-without-password

1. ssh-keygen -t rsa
Press enter for each line 
2. cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
3. chmod og-wx ~/.ssh/authorized_keys 

